Class ForLoop

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.integration.mwe2.mwe2impl.Sequence
      • org.eclipse.viatra.integration.mwe2.mwe2impl.ForLoop
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeStep, ITransformationStep

    public class ForLoop
extends Sequence
    Composite transformation step that implements a 'for' style loop. The number of iterations can either be explicitly specified at compile time, using the iterations attribute, or dynamically calculated by an IIterationNumberProvider.
